data.description: This 4 bed 2 bath home in the Wylie ISD district offers a spacious and versatile floor plan. With two dining areas, one of which can be used as an office or playroom, there is plenty of room for customization. The living area features a brick wall with a wood-burning fireplace, creating a cozy focal point. The split bedroom floor plan ensures privacy, and the bedrooms are nicely sized with ample closet space and storage throughout the home. The kitchen boasts granite countertops with under cabinet lighting, a glass front cabinet, built-in desk, and an island for added convenience. The master bedroom  has two walk-in closets, double sinks, a soaker tub, and a tiled shower. Additionally, this home is conveniently located near the fairway golf course, allowing residents to enjoy the beauty and recreational opportunities it offers.
